Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Tanyu been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you, the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She was writing for some time, \Nso she's resting right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here to view the archives again today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read most of the past generations' works, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're at Miss Tanyu's generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts from that shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and give me that thing... your cigar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to smoke in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never be too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,These are not merely guides to sealing away mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten that, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these are indisputably secret documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only for their contents,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but more so for their raison d'etre...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Forward: Circumstances regarding the birth of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanyu, fourth-generation scribe\N of the Karibusa family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recorded by Tama Minai, mushi-shi\N to the Karibusa family."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The black birthmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the fourth-generation scribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanyu-ojousan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play outside like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is studying how to read and write all I ever do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't this leg move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You are old enough now to understand, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you... everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That birthmark on your right leg is a remnant of mushi sealed away inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My mushi-shi ancestor sealed the forbidden mushi in your ancestor's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forbidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By nature, flora and fauna are in harmony with mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where flora and fauna flourish, so do mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where they die off, the mushi do, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But once upon a time, as flora, \Nfauna and mushi were dying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,following a terrible natural catastrophe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a different sort of mushi appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,One that attempted to erase all other life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that mushi like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No records have ever been found of its shape or form,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,or even how it was sealed inside her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The story passed down in my family is that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:07:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,your ancestor was pregnant when the mushi was sealed inside of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,causing her entire body to turn coal black...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The mushi continued to live inside her body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but she died after giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, Every few generations\N in the Karibusa family,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a child is born with a coal-black birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it's still alive in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to die soon, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to keep that from happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have the power to put\N the mushi to sleep for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will help you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have gotten a little \Nbetter at reading and writing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we will move to the country house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There, we will bury the forbidden\N mushi underground forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, your black birthmark will disappear and you will be able to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of your ancestors put the mushi to sleep that way little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a dream of long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The way to put mushi to sleep that Tama told me of later on was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please write down everything \NI am about to tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of Tama's stories were about how\Nshe defeated mushi as a mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They seemed like fantasy, but they were all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She described major roundups with dramatic flair
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and told sad stories by dim lantern light...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were stories of far away places \Nand unfamiliar people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every one of them always fascinated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, when I wrote them down, an intense pain ran through my birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the mushi leaving my body right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I have defeated many mushi\Nis a curse to the forbidden one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize it's painful, but please bear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you were forced to become a mushi-shi, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There must've been difficult times...\NYou must've begrudged your fate for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those feelings disappeared the first time I met you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I am grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How hard Tama was trying to ease my pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't until later on, when she ran out of stories
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and began inviting other mushi-shi \Nto tell theirs, that I realized it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And in order to wipe out the vermin mushi,\NI used its natural enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,this mushi here... and released huge numbers of them in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In less than a month, you couldn't \Neven find a vermin mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, of course, I destroyed these mushi, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have too many of them around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew how to get rid of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every one of the stories I heard was about killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pain in my leg was joined by a pain in my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Killing brought on by arrogance \Ntoward tiny, lower life forms
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and by unfounded fears of things\Ndifferent than themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was something I sensed very strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be a way without killing them, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that is something only one who has actually faced mushi should say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there was nothing I could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I could use this leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Might you be the daughter of the Karibusa family?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might be since there aren't any other houses around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is the black birthmark I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a mushi-shi, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're collecting stories about mushi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand if I co-operate, I can\N peruse the Karibusa archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough about killing mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll tell you stories about not killing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I happen to have many more of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But those won't be of use...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.47,Alt,,0,0,0,,Let me start with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A story about the mushi that eat moles...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Moles?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You were about to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your stories about mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you need Tama's permission first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tama probably wouldn't want \Nto hire a mushi-shi like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be very careful how you handle the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are mushi lying dormant in those character strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The forbidden mushi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't kill me that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this is quite a treasure for mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But everything in here is a record of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear more stories of animals \Nand mushi living together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll somehow convince Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So will you come and talk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss? Oh, you're already awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bookworm eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh... Here... and here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The character strings are beginning to come apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it... happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Otama-san! The bookworms are\Nstarting to eat the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal is gonna break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Tanyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The seal is partially broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry. They can't leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Still alive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... It's hard to believe that\Nthey had been dormant for centuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was talking about you, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem fazed... Can you return these things to the way they were?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a few mushi control methods as well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The character strings have stopped moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The walls and ceiling of this room\Nare covered with a special paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 1853, chapter one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You memorized the entire contents?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether there are bookworms or not, paper will eventually deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to copy the text from time to time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But just copying it in a normal \Nway doesn't seal the mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way of copying passed down in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bookworms are Miss Tanyu's pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sort of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they've proliferated a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay... as long as I make copies \Nin a proper way like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a dangerous pastime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't make mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,since this is, after all, my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a young woman who lives in a sea of writings as if she's drowning in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So is that "case closed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than half of what you told me\Nis useful for sealing away mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a hard day yesterday and\Nyou must be tired. Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko, stay there until I finish, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a young woman ravaged by mushi, who loves mushi while sealing them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please prepare her bedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine without rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go outside instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you take me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When will I ever be able to use this leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The birthmark is gradually getting smaller, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, though little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't get rid of it before I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,my descendants will inherit the birthmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as it's always been...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not happen in my lifetime, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do if your leg heals?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to travel with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To see the mushi you told me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the best case, I'll be an old lady by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, if...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm still alive and well at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know... I might be eaten by a mushi tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's asking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll manage somehow.
